terface needs to be done in a more interesting way from both appearance, audio, and content perspectives.In conclusion, although I cites the above cons, I do feel they exist because the Devs tried to do the right thing by presenting a solid game experience first, and worry about interface eye candy later, at least I hope so.Regardless, this game deserves such eye candy to be implemented asap, as it is a good game that deserves such polish.Hopefully, the lack of such eye candy will not hurt its early access sales.I purchased this game because i see great potential to take over the genre once the game is finished and out of early access, and thought $19 was a good price, as I can see the price going up upon release."
